{"tid":1732844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴正聲明：絕非ENDGAME！！！","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T18:27:52.000Z","uid":22796,"like":354,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"16ea5350ff8ea4baf330439beec96fb69d261d57","tid":1732844,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:28:20.000Z","msg":"見到出面班失敗撚 分化撚 都唔知嗰啲係真on9定mon po狗 我先屌晒佢哋老母 呢度係討論場革命要點行落去<br />\n<br />\n正題<br />\n出面有風吹 留喺埋大嘅都係勇武手足嚟 而且救到嘅成數唔大 當然救到人係最理想<br />\n我想講嘅係 如果真係冇咗大批勇武手足 和理非可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n全民進化會係一種出路<br />\n做得和理非唔出去做衝衝子 多數都係因為仲有底線 但你睇到對家係完全冇底線呢樣嘢 612到而家 姦殺 實彈殺人 放毒氣 呢啲一切都係要消滅真香港人 我哋要漸漸放低底線 唔好再做被動嘅一群<br />\n新手上路除咗買裝 可以練吓火魔法 之後再升級 當然去到殺警係最好<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以繼續提供方向 直到五大訴求完全被回應<br />\n<br />\n最後 勇武唔係condom<br />\n我哋唔可以辜負勇武一直以嚟嘅付出<br />\n<br />\n和理非表示：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我愛勇武</span></span>"},{"pid":"ecbbb8eceb104b4e85e587ca77098839745799a8","tid":1732844,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NdgS8Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NdgS8Y.jpg&h=fb14efa1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老豆搵仔呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去理大啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"},{"pid":"4d2639bb2a22fa040bcd6668945ab4b0fcdc840f","tid":1732844,"uid":229656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f28ea46de415ac92250d78257d0dc336f09893","tid":1732844,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99660d0de3be2ca0