yTime":"2019-11-18T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"成日都想知點解會覺得全港勇武係哂入面<br />\n入面有一部分係當初話要死守既死守撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"根本有人尻up 暴大個日好多傷左抖緊<br />\n同好多人根本入唔到去 何來全港勇武係哂入面<br />\n佢依家拎poly入面做人質狂拉救佢地既手足"},{"pid":"47f6c228bbf419eb8ff096d525c3dad57640e8fd","tid":1732844,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:24:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c2783832a571d79299c53424f30388765a7cd75d","tid":1732844,"uid":214640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0ec5c66d2ca16a58ce7f34f5cac438efa60e62","tid":1732844,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d29702d945238ee6f1ee08a02df9297ade09e9c","tid":1732844,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"出緊去<br />\n希望大家可以認真看待今晚<br />\n必要時 留住有用之軀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">煲底之約 不要忘記</span></span>"},{"pid":"a2f9ae2a128095b4837e6fd5e4a2ba313d5bf7ce","tid":1732844,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c29c2367ce110d1e11b15a7aa8d34d076e3ea35","tid":1732844,"uid":7549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22a7093539d64e06c90ae85375c2c217efdaa568","tid":1732844,"uid":126366,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"16ea5350ff8ea4baf330439beec96fb69d261d57","tid":1732844,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:28:20.000Z","msg":"見到出面班失敗撚 分化撚 都唔知嗰啲係真on9定mon po狗 我先屌晒佢哋老母 呢度係討論場革命要點行落去<br />\n<br />\n正題<br />\n出面有風吹 留喺埋大嘅都係勇武手足嚟 而且救到嘅成數唔大 當然救到人係最理想<br />\n我想講嘅係 如果真係冇咗大批勇武手足 和理非可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n全民進化會係一種出路<br />\n做得和理非唔出去做衝衝子 多數都係因為仲有底線 但你睇到對家係完全冇底線呢樣嘢 612到而家 姦殺 實彈殺人 放毒氣 呢啲一切都係要消滅真香港人 我哋要漸漸放低底線 唔好再做被動嘅一群<br />\n新手上路除咗買裝 可以練吓火魔法 之後再升級 當然去到殺警係最好<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以繼續提供方向 直到五大訴求完全被回應<br />\n<br />\n最後 勇武唔係condom<br />\n我哋唔可以辜負勇武一直以嚟嘅付出<br />\n<br />\n和理非表示：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我愛勇武</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"五毛想帶風向等大家覺得全部勇武瓜晒<br />\n然後想我哋覺得自己輸<br />\n頭腦清醒嘅就唔好俾佢帶到風向<br />\n第一<br />\n和理非隨時都可以轉做勇武<br />\n第二<br />\n邊個話最激進勇武係晒理大<br />\n第三<br />\n拉咗都未必有證據告得入<br />\n保釋踢保出返嚟照舊係勇武<br />\n第四<br />\n就算場運動暫時少咗勇武<br />\n都並不代表會輸<br />\n每次去到啲樽頸位我哋都能夠自我修正<br />\n搵到新嘅方法去突破<br />\n我相信今次都唔會例外"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72617f20d63ecda029fe77c898d4848868c8416","tid":1732844,"uid":310733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:32:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0bcaefd80b2d4eb4408af3a1c4f33b718926b053","tid":1732844,"uid":157077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"一陣見大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5e61ccd14592b5921a20e281b5fe3ae1a0c908","tid":1732844,"uid":101906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12afbce280535f0e771fb17ac71725ef39fdb8b0","tid":1732844,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52bdc58558114ae1bc42802616db2cf667471b91","tid":1732844,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:36:05.000Z","msg